data.description: Lovely split level home, with daylight basement. Recently remolded with all you need for great living! New kitchen with new stainless appliances &quartz counters w/open bright dining room. Wood burning fireplace on each floor, gas heat, large master with it's own bath & spacious bedrooms with lots of closet space. Features 1 full bath w/deep soaking tub, 3/4 bath off the master on main level + 1/2 bath on lower level. Laundry room w/plenty of storage and washer/dryer. Large finished room downstairs would make a great family /rec room or add a 4th bedroom. Landscaped backyard, private deck & fire pit for outdoor entertaining. Large 2 car garage with workspace.  Convenient location, close to shopping center and Costco. Mins to Hwy 99 & I5.
